    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions, required level 3, achieved level 2) is below the required level due to testing at a single load rate and environmental condition; this gap is accepted given the quasi-static nature of the loading, supporting literature on rate insensitivity of titanium constructs, and the MEDIUM model influence classification. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision. Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and has not been applied to this package.",
